title: Grateful Dead Live at Sportsahalle on 1990-10-24
description:
Set 1

Feel Like A Stranger, Cold Rain & Snow, Little Red Rooster, They Love Each Other, Me & My Uncle-> Big River, West L.A. Fadeaway, Queen Jane Approximately, Iko Iko

Set 2

Help On The Way-> Slipknot!-> Franklin's Tower, Truckin'-> He's Gone-> Drums-> Jam-> I Need A Miracle-> The Wheel-> Goin' Down The Road Feelin' Bad-> Around & Around, E: U.S. Blues
